cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper deals with fine-grained recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves using a hierarchy of pose-aligned regions, which requires machine learning techniques for classification (cs.LG) and potentially involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.MM) and the evaluation of the proposed method on two datasets (cs.IR).
